= Publications

Updated 2026. *Bold* = first author. Total: 2 Q1 journal papers, 9 IEEE peer-reviewed international conference papers, 1 award, 2 service appointments.

For the live citation count and any newer items, see my [https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=tHBBTIEAAAAJ Google Scholar profile].

